  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "body": "*Description*:\r\nWhen the envoy proxy is used as an ingress gateway for multiple endpoints/services it would be useful to set trace sampling parameters on a per service/endpoint basis. If defined, these would override the global values set at the filter level.\r\n\r\nProposal would be to add a trace sampling config to the [route](https://www.envoyproxy.io/docs/envoy/latest/api-v2/api/v2/route/route.proto#envoy-api-msg-route-route).\r\n\r\n",
